            <h2 class="rainbow-text">THE END?</h2>
            <div class="epilogue">
                <p class="narration">
                    <strong>EPILOGUE:</strong> M&LE1 went on to found the "Inner Child Institute," a nonprofit teaching emotional intelligence through AI-assisted music therapy. His TED talk "The Authenticity Paradox in a Post-Truth World" has been viewed 50 million times. He still can't legally buy alcohol in most metaverses.
                </p>
                <p class="narration" style="margin-top: 1rem;">
                    The debate over his "realness" continues, but his impact on a generation of digital natives is undeniable. As he once said in a now-famous tweet: <em>"I may be fake, but my feelings about being fake are real."</em>
                </p>
            </div>
            
