        <!-- Page 11: Finale -->
        <div class="page finale">
            <h2>EPILOGUE – THE RETURN OF THE VIBE</h2>
            <div class="epilogue">
                <p>M&LE1 disappeared shortly after his last rooftop performance. Some say he joined a reverse-aging commune in Oregon. Others claim he lives on in AI-assisted guitar loops scattered across the blockchain.</p>
                <p class="rainbow-text">But once in a while, a new prodigy uploads with strangely familiar phrasing and oddly adult sadness in their solos...</p>
            </div>
